1. *Svedoka* pokazuju da je on kriv. (The witnesses show that he is guilty.)
2. On je video *svedoka* u akciji. (He saw the witnesses in action.)
3. Tužilaštvo traži *svedoke* za suđenje. (The prosecution is asking for witnesses for the trial.)
4. Sud je zapitao *svedoke*. (The court questioned the witnesses.)
5. Oni su imali *svedoka* na njihovoj strani. (They had a witness on their side.)
6. *Svedočenje* je bilo dokaz koji je sud prihvatio. (The testimony was evidence accepted by the court.)
7. Oni su se oslanjali na *svedočenje* da bi dokazali svoju tvrdnju. (They relied on the testimony to prove their claim.)